{
  "stem": "13315.2",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But you spent it because you could have it also only up to a certain amount.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The money that I had before that was taken when I was arrested.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Then afterwards, Father-- every four or five weeks, he sent me some.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "That helped me to survive.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That was officially-- again, one every four or five weeks we could write, but that was an open letter, and they checked out what you wrote.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, get me out.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Get me out.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And hoping that they were well.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I tried one time in this one block where I tried to organize a discussion.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But it didn't work out, because everybody was concerned with himself.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I, myself, too.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Because as I say, the worst aspect of it was, you didn't know from one moment to the other what would happen.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] You were fully at the discretion of the SS.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, for example they started exercising us in the dirt.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And afterwards, we had to wash it first.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "In the mud, outside.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Things like that.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Where once, he was there-- a young SS man, we knew later that he was an SS man, in a uniform of one of the prisoners.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Maybe they just planted him.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Anyhow the freedom-- he tyrannized to no end to collect all his cigarette slips from the others, from the place there all over.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But we couldn't stand or something.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We had to go, how should I say?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We bent down.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And it could take an hour or two.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Just to humiliate everybody.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Pardon?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Not only humiliate, but it was a physical strain, too.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We saw only the one.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Which they showed to us.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But we knew that people always-- we didn't know did they disappear or did they-- were they released?",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    }
  ],
